videos.headline: Notre Dame strikes first with 18-yard TD reception to Finke
videos.description: Ian Book completes an 18-yard pass to Chris Finke who fights his way to the end zone to score a Notre Dame touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Notre Dame strikes first with 18-yard TD reception to Finke) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Book connects with Claypool for 2nd touchdown
videos.description: Ian Book throws his second touchdown pass of the night after connecting with Chase Claypool for the seven-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Book connects with Claypool for 2nd touchdown) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young hauls in 29-yard TD for Duke
videos.description: Duke gets its first touchdown of the game as Quentin Harris completes a pass to Aaron Young for a 29-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Young hauls in 29-yard TD for Duke) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Duke's Carter comes up with unlikely INT off a player's helmet
videos.description: Ian Book's pass is knocked down and bounces off a helmet as Michael Carter II slides in to scoop it up for an unlikely Duke interception at the one yard line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Duke's Carter comes up with unlikely INT off a player's helmet) 2019/11/09 ESHEET
